      <p>Weather data powers everything from travel apps and farming tools to logistics optimization and smart home automation. Whether you're building a simple weather widget or a complex agricultural forecasting system, there's a free API that fits your needs.</p>
      <p>The key differences between weather APIs come down to: <strong>data freshness</strong> (how often they update), <strong>historical depth</strong> (how far back you can query), <strong>geographic resolution</strong> (how precise the location data is), and <strong>free tier generosity</strong> (how many requests you get).</p>

